prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, clean flat 2D illustration. A cartoon version of Lao Lao, based on the reference photo, is sitting happily at a low minimalist table. A cartoon version of Jordan, based on the reference photo, is excitedly presenting her with a giant birthday "cake" made entirely of stacked sushi rolls, nigiri, and maki. The sushi cake is whimsically decorated with tiny party hats on some of the pieces. Two adorable, small cartoon dogs sit at Lao Lao's feet, looking up at the sushi with huge, hopeful eyes and wagging tails. The entire scene is set against a solid, soft pastel background with ample clean white space. Centered above the scene, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script. The composition is funny, charming, and focused on the couple and their shared interests.
